.env.prod
# FS-0031 — local e2e DB overlay (copy of .env → ronindojo_e2e); loaded via `bun --env-file=.env.e2e`.
# `.env.e2e.example` documents the shape; the real `.env.e2e` (real secrets) is NEVER committed.
.env.e2e

